<subSubSection id="71B960E8FFA73C738A91FDD7FC74FD1C" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="391C3363FFA73C738A91FDD7FC74FD1C" blockId="8.[151,1437,153,683]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis id="0BD7EF71FFA73C738A91FDD7FEF9FD30" bold="true" box="[199,353,620,647]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Distribution.</emphasis>
North Island, South Island. Most of the specimens in the NZAC are from the North Island; however, there is a small number of specimens of a new species from Fiordland.
</paragraph>
